<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forgot Password</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS styles for the email template */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 10px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #321fdb;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Forgot Password</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= firstName ? firstName+" "+lastName : username %>,</p>
        <p>You recently requested to reset your password. Click the button below to reset it:</p>
        <a href="<%= link %>" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
        <p>This is valid for 10 minutes</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this, you can ignore this email. Your password won't be changed unless you click the
            button above to reset it.</p>
        <p>Thanks,<br> Your COFAX BUSINESS SYSTEMS INC</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>